        Constructor for adding new parkEntry
        Parameters:
        entryType - can be {Personal, Subscriber, Group, PrivateGroup}
        personID - the ID of person who made the reservation
        parkID - ID of the park
        arriveTime - entry time to the park
        exitTime - exit time from the park
        numberOfVisitors - number of total visitors
        numberOfSubscribers - number of subscribers of total visitors
        isCasual - true only if its a casual visit (and not a registered order)
        price - the price of the entry
